@startuml
' --- IDENTITY REDIRECTION ---
' This diagram uses the Central Command Global Style.
' Path: tools/reporting/styles/cc_modern_theme.puml
!include ../../tools/reporting/styles/cc_modern_theme.puml

title Arquitectura Interna de jkanime Scraper (proj-037)

box "Entorno de Usuario" #DEECF9
    actor "Usuario" as U
    participant "CLI Interface\\n(argparse)" as CLI
end box

box "Lógica del Scraper (jkanime_scraper.py)" #FFF4CE
    participant "Core Engine\\n(httpx + re)" as S
    participant "Checkpoint Manager\\n(progress.json)" as CK
    database "Almacenamiento Local" as FS
end box

box "Servidores Externos" #FDE7E9
    participant "jkanime.net" as JK
    participant "Mediafire" as MF
    participant "Fallback Servers\\n(mp4upload, etc)" as FB
end box

== FASE 1: INICIALIZACIÓN ==

U -> CLI: Ejecuta python jkanime_scraper.py --url [URL]
CLI -> S: Inicializa motor con argumentos
S -> CK: Verifica estado previo (Resume)

== FASE 2: SCRAPING DE EPISODIOS ==

S -> JK: GET Episode HTML
activate S
JK --> S: HTML con 'var servers = [...]'
S -> S: decode_servers() (Base64 decode)

alt Mediafire Disponible (Prioridad 1)
    S -> MF: GET Mediafire Page URL
    MF --> S: Mediafire Direct URL (Signed)
    S -> CK: Guarda enlace directo
else Fallback yt-dlp
    S -> S: pick_fallback()
    S -> CK: Guarda URL de host (mp4upload, etc)
end

S -> CK: Actualiza progress.json
deactivate S

== FASE 3: GENERACIÓN DE ARTEFACTOS ==

S -> FS: Genera download.sh (wget/yt-dlp)
S -> FS: Genera links.json (Permanent + Temp)
S -> FS: Genera playlist.m3u

== FASE 4: DESCARGA (Ejecución de Usuario) ==

U -> FS: bash download.sh
activate FS
FS -> MF: Download MP4
MF --> FS: [1.mp4, 2.mp4...]
deactivate FS

legend bottom
|= Componente |= SSoT / Función |
| progress.json | Estado de extracción (Evita re-scraping) |
| download.sh | Automatización de descargas con reintentos |
| mediafire_pages.json | Enlaces permanentes para regenerar links expirados |
endlegend

@enduml
